messages.text: Who’s this? How did you get Mike’s number
Mia? What do you mean - It’s me, Mike!
Mike is in a coma. Whoever you are this isn’t funny. Just stop
STOP THIS. I’m sitting next to Mike in the hospital
But I can hear your voice
You are REALLY trying my nerves here
Mia it’s me! I’ll prove it to you:
I know about your sister being a lesbian …
Is it … is it really you?
But you’re right here … IN A COMA
This is incredible. So I text you … and you hear me?
What happened? Why am I in a coma?
We were in a car accident … You don’t remember?
Doctors said you might stay like this forever
It’s hard to explain … There is this clock
I just kind of know it’s there
I’m  … not sure. It just sort of feels like that
Oh no. How can that be? You’ve been stable for a while
I see something … or, sort of feel it
Oh god – if there is a strong white light, DON’T GO THERE
Wait there’s something written on the doors
Do you have to tell a lie to live?
Try to go through? I’m right here with you in the hospital if you wake up
It seems to be locked … But the clock started to go much FASTER
Yes, it’s at 15 hours already, going fast
Should I try the other door?
But that one says die … I don’t think you should do it
I don’t know oh god this is terrible
How did it all even happen
We were driving and someone crashed into us
I was ok but your side was badly beaten
There is a precipice behind it, I almost fell in
AND THE CLOCK IS GOING EVEN FASTER
Oh no no no no sorry sorry
Oh god your heartbeat just went crazy
I can see it on the machine
It’s at 10 hours now, and speeding up
I feel terrible. Last thing I said to you was a curse word
Wait, the other door JUST OPENED
Right after you said curse word …
It’s only open a crack … I can’t go in. But I can see a corridor
They are meant for ME, not you
Oh baby, I haven’t told you the exact truth
What do you mean? Clock says 5!!!
But just before that, we had a terrible fight
I was really mean to you … and I refused to drive
I should have been the one to get crushed
What are you talking about? It’s at 4 …
‘Lie and live’: don’t tell the truth and I live, but you die
I can fix this! I love you darling
Wait what? The other one is ‘die and let live’
Does that mean you die and I live??
THERE MUST BE SOME OTHER WAY
My darling, how could you do it?
You jumped into the river, and I woke up
They pulled you out, but your brain suffered a lack of oxygen
I’m gonna keep texting until you do
